{"tid":779183,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【宜蘭2日1夜】地道美食、住宿、交通","createTime":"2018-08-14T08:38:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T07:26:07.000Z","uid":199360,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b83405fdabaa6066c57fb2b6c45c5c74ba4ce04a","tid":779183,"uid":199360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T08:38:22.000Z","msg":"台灣去咗N咁多次，次次去親都係去台中台北高雄，嗰啲市區。今次去台北本身都唔諗住去其他城市，不過我比我個台灣fd打動咗去宜蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  極到臨時嘅行程，個台灣fd用咗兩日就plan好哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n台北搭自強號火車到東山站落車，約1.5小時，台幣184（單程）<br />\n火車時間表：<a href=\"http://twtraffic.tra.gov.tw/twrail/TW_Quicksearch.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwtraffic.tra.gov.tw%2Ftwrail%2FTW_Quicksearch.aspx&d=7%2FGlMB%2F%2B1qOC0kvt7OfS3J4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=f11184c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://twtraffic.tra.gov.tw/twrail/TW_Quicksearch.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n我哋住依間沐禾渡假會館，每人每晚HKD 328，嚮東山火車站搭的士四分鐘就到，好方便。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/153837_6b79565f344bafcc6bfe13c84a0059e1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F153837_6b79565f344bafcc6bfe13c84a0059e1.png&h=4ba49f11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網站：<a href=\"https://asiayo.com/zh-tw/view/tw/yilan-county/16685/?people=1&amp;check_in_date=2018-8-01&amp;check_out_date=2018-08-31&amp;cc=yilan_16685&amp;utm_source=comunity_hk_lihkg&amp;utm_medium=yilan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasiayo.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fview%2Ftw%2Fyilan-county%2F16685%2F%3Fpeople%3D1%26check_in_date%3D2018-8-01%26check_out_date%3D2018-08-31%26cc%3Dyilan_16685%26utm_source%3Dcomunity_hk_lihkg%26utm_medium%3Dyilan&d=7%2FGlMB%2F%2B1qOC0kvt7OfS3J4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=24de2a0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://asiayo.com/zh-tw/view/tw/yilan-county/16685/?people=1&amp;check_in_date=2018-8-01&amp;check_out_date=2018-08-31&amp;cc=yilan_16685&amp;utm_source=comunity_hk_lihkg&amp;utm_medium=yilan</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果冇記錯，依度係頭城海濱公園，望出去就係太平洋，好靚！見到依幕，覺得依程嚟係啱嘅，所謂step out your &quot;comfort zone&quot;，台北是我的comfort zone XD<br />\n果粒山叫龜山島，聽聞有人住島上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/155608_da0c1d98892df0bf9718fc4a25679c4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F155608_da0c1d98892df0bf9718fc4a25679c4d.jpg&h=b0377ad1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n宜蘭四大明湖，其中一個：望龍埤，簡直世外桃源。散下步，飲下珍珠奶茶，好涼好正！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/160257_de603e805628f5f46cd14642a73c2503.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F160257_de603e805628f5f46cd14642a73c2503.jpg&h=43a08ebe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/160357_3947b6818d7494952bed3ef3090f4169.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F160357_3947b6818d7494952bed3ef3090f4169.jpg&h=aa7de83e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n宜蘭海鮮好出名，此趟旅程最好食是這間 廟口海產，佢哋個酥炸蚵仔，食落有感動嘅感覺！<br />\n不過佢哋服務態度極差，好食都未必會再嚟。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/162102_893f739ac51f4129369cc95d0e08b4cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F162102_893f739ac51f4129369cc95d0e08b4cf.jpg&h=c19335a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有間瓜仔雞都好食，不過唔記得影相，如果有興趣可以睇依個blog，佢有介紹。<br />\n<a href=\"https://stayingfun.com/zh-tw/travelers-guide/tw/yilan-musteat\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstayingfun.com%2Fzh-tw%2Ftravelers-guide%2Ftw%2Fyilan-musteat&d=7%2FGlMB%2F%2B1qOC0kvt7OfS3J4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=3d144413\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://stayingfun.com/zh-tw/travelers-guide/tw/yilan-musteat</a>"},{"pid":"20e9d0010ece693d4af84975255d26e65bed7516","tid":779183,"uid":35746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T10:10:47.000Z","msg":"推，下次"},{"pid":"609262950472eab21ef83a671136724bfd7bbf69","tid":779183,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T10:36:41.000Z","msg":"lm準備去宜蘭 <br />\n 冇車冇fd , 好唔方便"},{"pid":"ba15c4ff2fab4e0daf787d36e790a2ec827449ed","tid":779183,"uid":199360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"609262950472eab21ef83a671136724bfd7bbf69","tid":779183,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T10:36:41.000Z","msg":"lm準備去宜蘭 <br />\n 冇車冇fd , 好唔方便"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T03:05:50.000Z","msg":"可以租電單車，唔洗有機車駕照都可以踩"},{"pid":"461106332be49c2dfb69aeac63a5aabf56415347","tid":779183,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"609262950472eab21ef83a671136724bfd7bbf69","tid":779183,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T10:36:41.000Z","msg":"lm準備去宜蘭 <br />\n 冇車冇fd , 好唔方便"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T05:13:34.000Z","msg":"我上次由台北坐客運到礁溪住一晚溫泉，第二日搭火車去宜蘭行幾米公園、新月廣場同宜蘭市內周圍搵嘢食，黃昏就搭火車去羅東夜市，食完就搭客運返台北，兩日一夜只用公共交通工具。"},{"pid":"ae96db989bcd69e166497be92e958a541e094756","tid":779183,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"461106332be49c2dfb69aeac63a5aabf56415347","tid":779183,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"609262950472eab21ef83a671136724bfd7bbf69","tid":779183,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T10:36:41.000Z","msg":"lm準備去宜蘭 <br />\n 冇車冇fd , 好唔方便"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T05:13:34.000Z","msg":"我上次由台北坐客運到礁溪住一晚溫泉，第二日搭火車去宜蘭行幾米公園、新月廣場同宜蘭市內周圍搵嘢食，黃昏就搭火車去羅東夜市，食完就搭客運返台北，兩日一夜只用公共交通工具。"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾米好似好多人話伏<br />\nbtw宜蘭好多博物館, 其實係咪都賣野多睇野少"},{"pid":"d6967f8d7809948252e093f9fd450d3f58394eee","tid":779183,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae96db989bcd69e166497be92e958a541e094756","tid":779183,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"461106332be49c2dfb69aeac63a5aabf56415347","tid":779183,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"609262950472eab21ef83a671136724bfd7bbf69","tid":779183,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T10:36:41.000Z","msg":"lm準備去宜蘭 <br />\n 冇車冇fd , 好唔方便"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T05:13:34.000Z","msg":"我上次由台北坐客運到礁溪住一晚溫泉，第二日搭火車去宜蘭行幾米公園、新月廣場同宜蘭市內周圍搵嘢食，黃昏就搭火車去羅東夜市，食完就搭客運返台北，兩日一夜只用公共交通工具。"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾米好似好多人話伏<br />\nbtw宜蘭好多博物館, 其實係咪都賣野多睇野少"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:56:23.000Z","msg":"對博物館冇興趣所以都冇去過，你要去既宜蘭市內都有巴士去晒主要景點的"},{"pid":"eb8b62bf749de2da0a650efa9402498291eb03f3","tid":779183,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae96db989bcd69e166497be92e958a541e094756","tid":779183,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"461106332be49c2dfb69aeac63a5aabf56415347","tid":779183,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"609262950472eab21ef83a671136724bfd7bbf69","tid":779183,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T10:36:41.000Z","msg":"lm準備去宜蘭 <br />\n 冇車冇fd , 好唔方便"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T05:13:34.000Z","msg":"我上次由台北坐客運到礁溪住一晚溫泉，第二日搭火車去宜蘭行幾米公園、新月廣場同宜蘭市內周圍搵嘢食，黃昏就搭火車去羅東夜市，食完就搭客運返台北，兩日一夜只用公共交通工具。"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾米好似好多人話伏<br />\nbtw宜蘭好多博物館, 其實係咪都賣野多睇野少"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:58:05.000Z","msg":"幾米公園其實都係同啲角色公仔影吓相打卡架咋，冇嘢玩，如果本身對幾米冇興趣就可能覺得伏既"},{"pid":"1a0d5a5e1b50e39f46f74ca86232e333db64bb79","tid":779183,"uid":199360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae96db989bcd69e166497be92e958a541e094756","tid":779183,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"461106332be49c2dfb69aeac63a5aabf56415347","tid":779183,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"609262950472eab21ef83a671136724bfd7bbf69","tid":779183,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T10:36:41.000Z","msg":"lm準備去宜蘭 <br />\n 冇車冇fd , 好唔方便"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T05:13:34.000Z","msg":"我上次由台北坐客運到礁溪住一晚溫泉，第二日搭火車去宜蘭行幾米公園、新月廣場同宜蘭市內周圍搵嘢食，黃昏就搭火車去羅東夜市，食完就搭客運返台北，兩日一夜只用公共交通工具。"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾米好似好多人話伏<br />\nbtw宜蘭好多博物館, 其實係咪都賣野多睇野少"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T00:18:28.000Z","msg":"幾米公園好細"},{"pid":"51fb514f55f80e8c698d7a5d5b2f1e4c6a7d4bd7","tid":779183,"uid":193239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T00:22:30.000Z","msg":"三星蔥, 櫻桃鴨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27baceb7c0e72396f0694d21a86d846b2e07e475","tid":779183,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T17:33:35.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"b47cc85de74117ab2777475a1cf819833a7eb2c9","tid":779183,"uid":113073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T07:26:07.000Z","msg":"幾米公園垃圾黎會坐火車經過就ok<br />\n<br />\n推介一定要去葛瑪蘭酒廠試酒<br />\n<br />\n4人起就食紅樓樓桃鴨（水準可能唔穩定）<br />\n<br />\n望龍埤其實普普通通，雙連埤正啲<br />\n<br />\n太平山、望晴懷古步道（全球28條最美步道之一）可以去（要包的士 / 自駕）<br />\n<br />\n櫻花陵園、福園（墓園）都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n宜蘭仲有好多步道都好正，易行，風景又唔錯"}]}